WITH "key_data_stats" AS (SELECT DISTINCT http_server_request.http_server_request ->> ?::text AS "request_method", http_server_request.http_server_request ->> ?::text AS "path_info" FROM "users_orgs", "scenarios", LATERAL jsonb_to_recordset(COALESCE(scenarios.events_http_server_requests, ?::jsonb)) http_server_request(id integer, http_server_request jsonb) WHERE (("scenarios"."org_id" = "users_orgs"."org_id") AND ("user_id" = ?))) SELECT count(*) AS "num_distinct" FROM "key_data_stats" LIMIT ?
